$interpreted: Deo: Rune, put me on your shoulders~ I wanna see the ocean!
Deo: Oh....still can't see.
Rune: What...do you want to see?
Deo: Across the ocean!
Deo: Rune, have you ever been on a boat?
Rune: Rune...doesn't remember.
Deo: You don't look like you're from the Desert Kingdom, so...
Deo: ...you must have!
Deo: I'm not jealous! I'll get on a boat someday! That way I can get out there and go on an adventure...
Rune: You are already...out there.
Deo: I mean the other side of the ocean!
Deo: My teacher told me there's a whole other world over there.
Deo: She said she'd take me...but she just up and left. Adults are always lying...
Rune: She...left...?
Deo: Forget her! She's not important, I don't care!
Robert: Deo, there you are!
Deo: Father...
Robert: So you're skipping school. How embarassing. Get home NOW!
Deo: Bu-But the new teachers treat me so bad. If I don't finish my homework, they won't let me eat or sleep.
Deo: They just hit me and yell at me...
Robert: You don't study and you're not that bright. They ought to punish you!
Robert: Do you know how expensive these private tutors are? Why can't you see how hard this is on me!?
Robert: Who the hell are you? Get out of my way!
Rune: Master Deo...is scared. Rune...must protect him!
Robert: Rune? You look familiar...
Robert: You're the victor from the Colosseum!
Robert: Hahaha! Magnificent! Deo, you've done well!
Deo: Huh...what's the Colosseum?
Robert: Useless fools! Get him!
Deo: Father, I'm sorry! I'll go home right now! I'll listen to you and won't skip school ever again!
Robert: Brat! Step away! Do you know how valuable this slave is?
Rune: ...*growl*...
Robert: I knew these guys wouldn't be able to restrain you. I mean, they couldn't even stop you at the Colosseum.
Robert: I want him alive! He's gonna make me big money!
Robert: Useless!
Deo: Rune, no!
Robert: He...hehe. So he'll listen to you!
Robert: Order him to let me go!
Deo: Ru...Rune...let him go...you can't hurt him...that's an order!
Rune: Rune...obeys Master Deo...
Robert: Hmph! That's right.
Robert: You think you can hit me! Don't you know your place!?
Deo: Father! Please don't hit him!
Robert: Deo, didn't he just call you master? Take a good look! As master, you've got to teach these slaves a lesson!
Rune: ...*growl*...
Deo: *sob*...Rune...sorry...*sob*...
Robert: You baby! What good are you? It's all that teacher's fault! Thought she was the ambassador of justice or some such nonsense!
Robert: Let's go home! Next time you run off, I'll beat you senseless!
